      "settings": {
        "subheading": "",
        "title": "",
        "html": "<div class=\"row center-xs\">\n\n<div class=\" col-xs-10 col-md-10 text--center\" style=\"padding-bottom:20px;\"> <span class=\"heading heading--large font-california-coast\">the results are in</span>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-3\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-6\" style=\"text-align:left; padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:20px;\">\n\n<p>Users reported seeing real results, including significant improvement in fine lines after just 4 weeks, more hydrated skin, and noticeable improvement in skin texture.*\n\n<br><i>*Clinical testing after 4 weeks of use</i></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-3\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1515/0462/files/FY-Gravity-Rebound-Serum-BA4.jpg?v=1724801004\" alt=\"before &amp; after\">\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1515/0462/files/FY-Gravity-Rebound-Serum-BA2.jpg?v=1724801004\" alt=\"before &amp; after\">\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1515/0462/files/FY-Gravity-Rebound-Serum-BA1.jpg?v=1724801004\" alt=\"before &amp; after\">\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1515/0462/files/FY-Gravity-Rebound-Serum-BA3.jpg?v=1724801003\" alt=\"before &amp; after\">\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
